      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――怜の誕生日企画前日　放課後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day before Rei's birthday project‚ after school",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1999.9999284,
          "startTime": 1.9999999284
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "中等部のみなさん、失礼します\nすず、いるわよね？　一緒に帰るわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me‚ everyone in middle school.\nSuzu‚ you're here‚ right? Let's go home together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8999999602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.8999999602
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.4333330552
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっとなんなんですの！？\n教室では静かにしてくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what are you doing?!\nPlease be quiet in the classroom!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0333332936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.9666680414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "すずの声の方が大きいわよ！\nほら、それより早く帰る準備して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your voice is louder‚ Suzu!\nCome on‚ get ready to go home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9000007231,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.4000013748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "あと十数時間後には、テーマパークに入るんだから\n忘れ物がないように、しっかり準備を整えないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll be entering the theme park in ten hours‚\nso we have to be prepared and make sure we don't forget anything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.1666673898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.5666680414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "気合いは分かりましたけど、落ち着いてくださいまし\nそんなに焦っても集合時間まで全然余裕が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know you're excited‚ but please calm down.\nEven if we rush‚ there's still plenty of time before the meeting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5333340565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2666670242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "何事も早め早めに動くことが肝心なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's important to get a head start on things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2666670242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.700002392
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "早めに動くことは大切ですが、さすがに早過ぎますわ！\n怜が楽しみな気持ちは十分伝わりましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I agree that getting a head start is important‚ but this is too early!\nI understand you're looking forward to it‚ Rei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7666673898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.1333357254
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "……一週間前からずっとカウントダウンしてましたし\n当日のテンションはもっと凄いことになりそうですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "… You've been counting down for a week‚\nand I wonder how excited you'll be on the actual day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4333340565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.1666680414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "何か言った？　喋ってたら三分もロスしちゃったわよ\n芽衣も迎えに行くんだから。ほら、早く",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you say something? We've already lost three minutes talking.\nWe have to pick up Mei too. Come on‚ hurry up!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9000007231,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4439.98884989999,
          "startTime": 74.339989573
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.6666695673
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.4666668812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、そんなに急かさないで……\nお待ちなさい、廊下を走ったらダメですわよー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ don't rush me too much…\nHold on‚ you shouldn't run in the hallway~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.4666668812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 82.3833387772
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 82.3833387772
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "今日明日と二日間の撮影になりますが\nよろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll be filming for two days‚ today and tomorrow‚\nso please take care of us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.833330496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 88.6000054438
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに素敵なホテル、それに料理やケーキも用意して\n下さり、本当にありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you so much for not only preparing this wonderful hotel‚\nbut also the food and the cake!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.5999971627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 95.8666721105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "良かったですわね、怜\n……さあ、カメラマンさん、準備はよろしいでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good for you‚ Rei.\n…Well then‚ cameraman‚ are you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9666638294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "実は、芽衣達からもお祝いがありまーす！\nいくよ、すずにゃん！　せーのっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ Mei and Suzu-nyan have a surprise for you~!\nHere we go‚ Suzu-nyan! One‚ two…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.5666637579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 111.5423417488
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お誕生日おめでとう！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Happy birthday!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.5423417488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00",
      "startTime": 112.4666647751
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
